@startuml
title 코드 마켓 시스템 유스케이스 (상위)

left to right direction

actor "회원" as Member
actor "결제 게이트웨이" as PG

rectangle "코드 마켓 시스템" {

  usecase "회원가입" as UC_Signup
  usecase "로그인" as UC_Login
  usecase "상품 검색" as UC_SearchProduct
  usecase "장바구니 추가" as UC_AddToCart
  usecase "주문" as UC_Order
  usecase "결제" as UC_Pay
  usecase "프로필 수정" as UC_EditProfile
  usecase "내 주문 내역 조회" as UC_ViewOrders
  usecase "내 장바구니 목록 조회" as UC_ViewCart

}

Member --> UC_Signup
Member --> UC_Login
Member --> UC_SearchProduct
Member --> UC_AddToCart
Member --> UC_Order
Member --> UC_Pay
Member --> UC_EditProfile
Member --> UC_ViewOrders
Member --> UC_ViewCart

' 결제 하위 플로우는 별도 다이어그램에서 상세화 (여기선 단순 연관만 표현)
UC_Pay ..> PG : 결제 승인/거절 연동

@enduml
